<strong><span style="color: #FF0000">READINGS IN AMAL QURANI OF MAULANA ASHRAF ALI THANWI<br /><br />PART 9</span></strong><br /><br />Yasir Jahmi talks about the chains of hadith and the Asha'airah when his forefathers were busy dishing advice to experiment with eggs for infertility.<br /><br />It upsets us that after 1400 centuries of academic exposure by Ahlus Sunnah in regards to the exposition and expounding of the Salafi creed, these born again deobandis have come with this argument asharis in the chain. What an absolute shambles and a disgrace to the hanafi deobandi ashari jahmi insurgency, is this is what you can come up with.<br /><br />As a point to reflect upon name one ashari in the chains to the compilers of hadith, as for the chains after well who cares even if it's tantamount to ijazahs. This clearly shows the asharis madhab is an innovation.<br />Back on point, egg protein for infertility let Yasir Jahmi ask his Ashari church father Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanwi about the following<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0040">FOR CHILDBIRTH<br /><strong>AYAH<br />whoever cannot bear children should boil two (2) eggs and then remove the shell and write the following ayahs on them. Then give one to the potentially infertile man and potentially infertile woman to eat. Continue this practise for 40 days and maintain a close physical relationship inshaAllah pregnancy will take place.b(Amal Qurani pp.30-31 of Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanwi and endorsed by Mufti Muhammad's Shafi, Mawlana Taqi Usmanis Father</strong></span></span><br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=130" class="postimage" alt="12841312_782901361854851_4143594234110513826_o.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=131" class="postimage" alt="10464235_782901318521522_7430569311723859755_n.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Sat Apr 01, 2017 2:16 pm</p><hr />
