<strong><span style="color: #FF0000">READINGS IN AMAL QURANI OF MAULANA ASHRAF ALI THANWI<br /><br />PART 8</span></strong><br /><br />One way ticket to paradise and all the gates to hell closed. The forefathers of Yasir Jahmi and his cohorts has assumed the position of Pope for the deobandis and behaving typically like a sufi church father.<br />In fact these deobandis are worse because the Christian priests promise their flock paradise after their confession and repentance but here the deobandi elders is informing us of the gates of hell closing for someone ie he will enter paradise. If they say it does not mean that then they adopted the mutazili belief of manzilah bayna manzilatain. Well nothing different there as deoband just returns to their founding school ie of eitizal<br /><br />He says<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0000">SALVATION FROM HELL<br />Whoever reads these 7 Haa mims then the 7 door of hell will be closed for him. (Amal Qurani pp.30 of Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanwi and endorsed by Mufti Muhammad's Shafi, Mawlana Taqi Usmanis Father</span></span></strong><br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=129" class="postimage" alt="12832289_780771192067868_3250896652609864047_n.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Sat Apr 01, 2017 2:14 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
