<strong><span style="color: #FF0040">READINGS IN AMAL QURANI OF MAULANA ASHRAF ALI THANWI<br /><br />PART 6</span></strong><br /><br />The forefathers of Mohammed Yasir Jahmi and Ibn Nur al-Shanti, Maulana Ashraf Ali Thanwi auzubillah mentioning another for the people to desecrate the Kalam of Allah,<br /><br />Subhanallah totally forgot these deluded Ashari Jahmi's don't even believe in the Kalam of Allah so how will they ever honour and revere the beautiful words of our creator<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0000">Maulana Thanwi mentions another yet another ayah women can write and place on their private parts in order to preserve their pregnancies (Amal Qurani pp.26)</span></span></strong><br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=127" class="postimage" alt="12716385_774181349393519_5276782170655747911_o.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><br /><br />He is referring to the following method in the passage<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0000">If the (woman) fails to get pregnant or she fears the pregnancy will not last then write both this ayah and the previous one and tie it to the woman's private part, inshaAllah tala her pregnancy will be preserved and she will remain pregnant if it was not holding. (Amal Qurani pp.24)</span></span></strong><br /></div></blockquote><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Sat Apr 01, 2017 2:04 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
